{title: Morning Song}

{start_of_verse}
[G]Wake up in the [C]morning light
[D]Everything is [G]bright
[Em]Coffee brewing [C]on the stove
[D]Another day to [G]love
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]Good [G]morning, [D]world
[C]Good [G]morning, [D]sun
[C]Good [G]morning [D]every[G]one
{end_of_chorus}

{new_song}

{title: Evening Song}

{start_of_verse}
[Am]Stars are coming [Dm]out tonight
[E]Moon is shining [Am]bright
[F]Crickets singing [C]in the dark
[E]Fireflies like [Am]sparks
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[Dm]Good [Am]evening, [E]world
[Dm]Good [Am]evening, [E]moon
[Dm]Good [Am]evening [E]see you [Am]soon
{end_of_chorus}
